{"tid":2408394,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"Ciao~☆ 澳洲 visa 最多 5 年，加國 visa 免審查，美國拒優先香港人","createTime":"2021-02-15T02:00:46.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-15T10:08:41.000Z","uid":36383,"like":6,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"432de5d7977ec4bbd9df5b345649b41f96ee16b8","tid":2408394,"uid":36383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-15T02:00:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 早排連登仔先講：香港難民，全球 welcome。結果接二連三咁發生利淡消息<br />\n<br />\n1. Ted 囝 ban 咗美國兩黨共識港人法案，未 ban 前 CC TOY 巴打吹到實 pass<br />\n<br />\n2. Biden (小敗敗) 上台，未完前 CC TOY 愛侵力袁爸帶風向<br />\n<br />\n3. 澳洲為港人 prolong 5 年 visa ，CC TOY 吹到為 PR pave way 係一定會批 PR 入籍，結果袋鼠國叫你地 5 年避完排返大隊，繼續技術移民<br />\n<br />\n4. CC TOY 不久前吹到咩政府工宣誓後冇移民，轉頭加拿大駐港話沒呢回事，對香港政府宣誓可以照移民因為加拿大認雙重國籍<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/plan.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/plan.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/plan.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/scheme.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 屌你班 CC TOY 風向撚仲燈過蕭山，假消息/個人幻想放落時事台不如縮返入政事台啦，害死香港移民後生囝"},{"pid":"a064ee930972368c170c39b2531de42d0f80f9b7","tid":2408394,"uid":36383,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-15T02:01:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 時事台班垃圾會員鳩嗚當秘笈，亂帶風向仲勁過五毛，人無知真可怕"},{"pid":"06aa895e5a45e83feeffcbaeaf199a1cb14f701f","tid":2408394,"uid":191926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-15T02:03:22.000Z","msg":"貼中拜登奶共  <br />\n已經夠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d608da5a2bfc12c01ac6744052f46c6b745ee8d0","tid":2408394,"uid":36383,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-15T02:04:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/arrogant.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/arrogant.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 時事台唔去放新聞，反而走去宣傳個人未經證實嘅幻想，由高登到連登一大陋習也。係人嘅問題，CC TOY 會然本身低汁唔關五毛事，冇曬五毛同 PR 都係不斷炒車 (思古并/假手足籌錢 etc.)"},{"pid":"d8d36e3ef9cf8f6a3fe8bbf69591eff91623385e","tid":2408394,"uid":36383,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"06aa895e5a45e83feeffcbaeaf199a1cb14f701f","tid":2408394,"uid":191926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-15T02:03:22.000Z","msg":"貼中拜登奶共  <br />\n已經夠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-15T02:05:57.000Z","msg":"小敗敗同小習習傾電話仲多過我同 Miss Pun 傾，冇鬼就假"},{"pid":"4c05ca7bb851f29bdde6590f8ddf8ad828f3321b","tid":2408394,"uid":36383,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-15T02:08:10.000Z","msg":"成個時事台充斥失實假新聞同個人憶測，不如歸入政事台算。有咩評論應該 #2 樓開始覆，標題同一樓內容應該中立同quote source <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 呢個係基本 journalism practice"},{"pid":"00d1e8676ecec8acb531dc2e9ea1a2fc96c7f48e","tid":2408394,"uid":31125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-15T10:08:41.000Z","msg":"高質移民=冇專業技能，英文Ielts冇7.5<br />\n高質移民=老馮要人收<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n講就高質移民 查實就一班離開左香港就搵唔到錢既港版中東移民<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}],"pinned":{"pid":"4c05ca7bb851f29bdde6590f8ddf8ad828f3321b","tid":2408394,"uid":36383,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-15T02:08:10.000Z","msg":"成個時事台充斥失實假新聞同個人憶測，不如歸入政事台算。有咩評論應該 #2 樓開始覆，標題同一樓內容應該中立同quote source <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 呢個係基本 journalism practice"}}